Input.text_9: The vinyasa flow class I attended today by Monika was perfect. It was a well paced class with great cues. I felt great after the class and feel it was well worth the 22 mile drive to get to the studio from where I was staying. Thanks!
Input.text_10:
I don't understand these low scores by the reviewers. This restaurant with its combination of price/ selection/quality and service is simply awesome. I come here for dinner regularly, w. two-three people party. We never had a bad meal
here.
Input.text_11: He has been my Thyroid specialist for years and his choice of medication seems to be working fine. I never have to wait long for my scheduled appointments. He is very professional and a caring doctor. He is the best.
Input.text_12: Very nice! Authentic flavors of Osaka! Inexpensive items on the menu and the music is hip hop which I grew up on. Decor is cute. I will be back again to try other things on the menu. I had the okonomiyaki!
Input.text_13: Ordered delivery. Food came 24 min after we ordered. Idk who made my pizza and bread, but that shit was fire!! It may have been the best Howie's pizza I've had. I mean it was perfect.. wings on the other hand. Meh. But everything else was on point! Thank you
Input.text_14: Place is a great place for lunch.  I'm not a big pie lover but when I have a craving this is a great place that has a lot of variety.  Ive tried most flavours and like them all.  The service is also fantastic .  And you can frozen ones too!

Input.text_17: I work close by to this panda express it's a accessible on their quick with their service at the drive-in I love the drive-in in fact on makes it so I can get back to work on time the food is excellent bus services fast thank you
Input.text_18: Food truck in front of Canadian Tire store. Have always wanted to stop for fries. Today was the day. Got poutine. Healthy portion. Only $5.75  truck was very tidy. Clean. Quick. Fresh. Friendly. Reasonable prices. Choose from hot dog, sausage, fries, poutine  & drink. We'll be back!
Input.text_19:
Deborah and her team of 1 are awesome!

I was able to rent a place in their very secure and monitored storage facility.

I know that my wine is safe, cool and available to me any time I need to access it.
Input.text_20: Maria Elena is wonderful! I can't say enough good things about the services she provides. I have had facials, microdermabrasion, and peels. She adds an extra touch by giving a neck and head massage! I wish I could give more than 5 stars. You won't be disappointed.
Input.text_21: Recently my husband visited the Scottsdale location and they have been absolutely amazing. The staff is so nice and personable and you can tell really cares for there clients. We recommend Peak Health Group in all aspects from the procedure to the staff. AMAZING and definitely give a big thumbs up. Thank you guys!
Input.text_22: AMAZING!  Great service.  Great knowledge. The tour guild drew is amazing.   It was so fun.  Everyone in this industry was so nice and accommodating.  We can't wait until we can tour an actually cultivation place, which we hear is next.   Thank again.
Input.text_23: This is one of my all-time favourite restaurants.  The dim-sum is the raison d'etre for this place, make sure you don't miss the sticky rice in leaf or the curry squids (oh yeah, that's how they spell it).  While I haven't had much of it, their regular chinese food has always been solid.
Input.text_24:
I went there for dinner with my family last week and they all like the food in this japanese restaurant.

Food: Sashimi (fresh), Assorted Tempura (Excellent), Sukiyaki Undon (Good)

Service: Chief and waiters are all japanese. (Polite)

I definitely will go back there!

Conveniently located in Westgate Resort and Casino,this Pizza Hut is a great express value meal for hotel guest... the are located right in front of north tower entrance of the resort...

Wonderful food combinations - the Mulligatawny was exceptional and the Cornish Hen flavour fusion very nice - provide excellent choices for both the adventuresome and seekers of an excellent Alberta beef experience.  Highly recommended,  excellent service,  beautiful and unique food choices in an understated environment. Go
Input.text_14: My ex-favorite shoe shine in Nashville better up their game.  The 9 step process renewed my winter worn favorite airport dress shoes.  He took great care and it felt like a massage for the tops of my feet.  Shiny, shiny, shiny.  A bargain at $5, but give him $10 or more.

Input.text_16: Great food last night.  We had Chicken Parmesan & Salmon Picatta!  Lovely wine, the girls had cannolis for dessert,  & Dad had coffee - black. The sign says Fine Dining, and it's the truth. If you haven't been in, I strongly recommend that you experience this restaurant & bar.

My only gripe is that I was told by staff that they do not accept manufacturers coupons.  In this economy every nickel counts so I can't give them five stars.  Love their hummus-yum.
Input.text_22: This is a great place to get lunch if you work in the area. Tons of lunch specials for under $7. I got a meal with sushi, soup, salad, orange slices, and egg rolls. The waitress was extremely nice and helpful! I will go back soon!

The food isn't THAT good to help rescue this restaurant from this review

Awesome service!!

Pizzas were fresh and always a great price!

Takes forever to get food. We were the only people there and we were told the reason they messed up 2 of our orders were due short staff.
